<div id="app" class="row">
    <input type="hidden" id="campaign_code" value="<%=campaign_code%>">
    <input type="hidden" id="bpType" value="<%=bpType%>">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
            <div class="wizard">
                <a class="current" href="/icampaign/write/<%=bpType%>/<%=campaign_code%>"><span class="badge badge-inverse">1</span> 설문등록</a>
                <% if(campaign_code != "") { %>
                <a href="/icampaign/sqWrite/<%=bpType%>/<%=campaign_code%>"><span class="badge">2</span> 선정 질문</a>
                <a href="/icampaign/resultSetting/<%=bpType%>/<%=campaign_code%>"><span class="badge">3</span> 결과 설정</a>
                <a href="/icampaign/qWrite/<%=bpType%>/<%=campaign_code%>"><span class="badge">4</span> 질문 설정</a>
                <a href="/icampaign/joinSetting/<%=bpType%>/<%=campaign_code%>"><span class="badge">5</span> 참여 설정</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!--
    <div class="push-10-t col-xs-12 bg-white box round_box_title">
        <div class="title"><span class="color">설문제목 : 사무용품 브랜드에 대한 이미지 조사 1차 2017</span></div>-
    </div>
    -->
    <div class="push-10-t col-xs-12 bg-white box round_box">

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-10 title">
                <span class="color">설문 기본정보</span>
                <div class="sub">설문 리스트에서 참여자에게 보여질 설문의 제목과 설명을 입력해주세요</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contents_list">
            <table id="list" class="table table-bordered fontsize">
                <col width="10%">
                <col width="90%">
                <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <th>설문제목(국문)</th>
                    <td>
                        <input type="text" id="campaign_title" class="form-control" value="<%=campaign_title%>">
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>설문제목(영문)</th>
                    <td>
                        <input type="text" id="campaign_title_en" class="form-control" value="<%=campaign_title_en%>">
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>설문제목(중문)</th>
                    <td>
                        <input type="text" id="campaign_title_cn" class="form-control" value="<%=campaign_title_cn%>">
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>설문설명(국문)</th>
                    <td>
                        <input type="text" id="campaign_desc" class="form-control" value="<%=campaign_desc%>">
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>설문설명(영문)</th>
                    <td>
                        <input type="text" id="campaign_desc_en" class="form-control" value="<%=campaign_desc_en%>">
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>설문설명(중문)</th>
                    <td>
                        <input type="text" id="campaign_desc_cn" class="form-control" value="<%=campaign_desc_cn%>">
                    </td>
                </tr>

                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="push-10-t col-xs-12 bg-white box round_box">

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-10 title">
                <span class="color">시작페이지</span>
                <div class="sub">설문시작페이지를 입력해주세요.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contents_list">
            <!-- Summernote Container -->
            <div id="startPage"><%-startPage%></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 bg-white box round_box push-10-t">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 title">
                <span class="color">설문기간 설정하기</span>
                <div class="sub">참여자가 설문에 참여할 수 있는 기간을 선택해주세요 종료 이후에는 설문 결과를 제출받지 않게 됩니다. 종료일시를 9999-12-31 23:59:59로 설정하게 되면 사용자에게는 '종료시까지'로 표시됩니다.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contents_list">
            <table id="list" class="table table-bordered fontsize">
                <col width="10%">
                <col width="40%">
                <col width="10%">
                <col width="40%">
                <tbody>
                <tr>

                    <th class="text-center">시작일시</th>
                    <td>
                        <div class="js-datetimepicker input-group date" data-show-today-button="true" data-show-clear="true" data-show-close="true" data-side-by-side="true">
                            <input class="form-control input-group-addon" type="text" id="campaign_startdate" placeholder="시작일시를 입력해주세요." value="<%=campaign_startdate%>">
                            <span class="input-group-addon"><span class="fa fa-calendar"></span></span>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <th class="text-center">종료일시</th>
                    <td>
                        <div class="js-datetimepicker input-group date" data-show-today-button="true" data-show-clear="true" data-show-close="true" data-side-by-side="true">
                            <input class="form-control input-group-addon" type="text" id="campaign_enddate" placeholder="종료일시를 입력해주세요."  value="<%=campaign_enddate%>">
                            <span class="input-group-addon"><span class="fa fa-calendar"></span></span>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th class="text-center">목표인원</th>
                    <td>
                        <input type="text" id="joinCnt" class="form-control" value="<%=joinCnt%>">
                    </td>
                    <th class="text-center">포인트제한</th>
                    <td>
                        <!--
                        <div class="col-xs-12">총 포인트 <input type="text" class="form-control"></div>
                        -->
                        <table>
                            <col width="20%">
                            <col width="30%">
                            <col width="20%">
                            <col width="30%">
                            <tr>
                                <td class="text-center">총 포인트</td>
                                <td><input type="text" class="form-control" id="totalPoint" value="<%=pointLimit%>"></td>
                                <td class="text-center">완료 포인트</td>
                                <td><input type="text" class="form-control" id="finishPoint" value="<%=finishPoint%>"></td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                </tbody>

            </table>
        </div>
    </div>




    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-6 push-20-t push-20">
            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-block btn-primary backBtn">이전</button>
        </div>

        <div class="col-xs-6 push-20-t push-20 text-right">
            <button v-on:click="campaignWrite" class="btn btn-sm btn-block btn-danger">저장</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



<!-- Page JS Plugins -->
<script src="/assets/js/plugins/summernote/summernote.min.js"></script>

<script language="javascript" src="/view_js/icampaign/write.js"></script>


